  "texts": [
    "These psychological phenomena describe a shared way of understanding and navigating the real world -sometimes referred to in terms of \"common ground\" and alignment of \"frames of reference. \"",
    "See for example (Allan, 2013; Fields et al., 2021; Friston et al., 2022).",
    "This makes intuitive sense, as all police officers at some point will arrest people, stop cars, and enter violent situations.",
    "These experiences are not rare and make up a very normal day for the average uniform police officer in any corner of the world.",
    "However, they are not shared by other professions who do not experience physiological and cognitive reactions to entering such encounters."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "See for example (Allan, 2013; Fields et al., 2021; Friston et al., 2022)."
  ]
}